Computes catch estimate

Source: R/artfish_compute_catch_estimate.R
compute_catch_estimate.Rd

Computes catch estimate

Usage

compute_catch_estimate(effort_estimate, landings, minor_strata = NULL)

Arguments

effort_estimate

effort estimate computed with compute_effort_estimate

landings

landings

minor_strata

minor_strata. Default is NULL

Value

a tibble giving the estimated catch by strata
